=======
LEGEND
=======

. = Background
# = Wall
P = Player
* = Cell
@ = Cell and Target
O = Target
c = Cord
u = CordUp
d = CordDown
l = CordLeft
r = CordRight

=======
SOUNDS
=======

================
COLLISIONLAYERS
================

Background
Target
Player, Wall, Cell, Cord, CordUp, CordDown, CordLeft, CordRight

======
RULES     
======     

[ >  Player | Cell ] -> [  >  Player | > Cell  ]     

==============
WINCONDITIONS
==============

All Target on Cell

