message Welcome to the future.

message LIFECOIN is a cryptocurrency that is tied directly to your mortality. When you run out of LIFECOIN -- you die.

message LIFECOIN is generated by complex machines that require tremendous power.

message You are on your last LIFECOIN.

message You find an abandoned LIFECOIN mine. If you can reinstall all of the power cores you may be able to generate enough LIFECOIN to live a long and comfortable life.

